#: creator/qml/WelcomePage.qml:71
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Longer introduction text used on the welcome page"
msgid ""
"Welcome to Peruse Creator, a tool designed to assist you in creating comic "
"book archives which can be read with any cbz capable comic book reader app. "
"You can either create entirely new comic book archives from scratch, create "
"one from a set of pictures, or editing existing archives. Once you have "
"created them, you can even publish them directly to the online comic book "
"archive at the KDE Store from within the application, or just share the "
"files with your friends."
msgstr ""
"Benvenite a Peruse Creator, un instrumento designate pro adjutar te a crear "
"archivos de libros de Comics que pote esser legite con qualcunque "
"applicationde lector de libros de Comics capace de cbz. Tu pote o crear "
"archivos de libros  de Comics integremente nove ab le initio, crear un ab un "
"gruppo de imagines,  o editar archivos existente. Un vice que tu los ha "
"create, tu pote mesmo publicar  los directemente al archivo de libros de "
"Comics in linea al KDE Store desde intra  le application, o simplemente "
"compartir le files con tu amicos."

